{"tid":2157526,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚惠珠：黎智英被捕與言論自由無關","createTime":"2020-08-15T05:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T06:58:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"89a784ed46234eed8e8038cf5e1407061e9eae9d","tid":2157526,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英及多名高層周一（10日）被警方以涉嫌違反《港區國安法》及串謀欺詐等罪名拘捕，百多名警員到壹傳媒大樓內蒐證。<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠今日（15日）出席商台節目稱，因案件已進入法律程序，不便評論詳情，但指出時至今日該集團旗下報章沒有被禁止出版，認為案件與言論自由無關。<br />\n<br />\n譚惠珠稱，在《港區國安法》生效下，市民應該謹言慎行，然而當政府出現失誤時亦應「該說就說」，但言論不能令政府不能正常運作，或使政權改變，亦不能外國制裁香港。"},{"pid":"0f29e1a2e6099c665e96435409cd168736457dc9","tid":2157526,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200815/s00001/1597464208778/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200815%2Fs00001%2F1597464208778%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8fLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=3808fc7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200815%2Fs00001%2F1597464208778%2F&h=19f5f344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200815/s00001/1597464208778/</a>"},{"pid":"0e6ca71734b467fba4e2719a95b2a0914e7d1887","tid":2157526,"uid":605,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"由你把閪口講出嚟咪即係代表同自由有關"},{"pid":"cd126081c162f3661021532dd2f701acd54eebcc","tid":2157526,"uid":245409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0f29e1a2e6099c665e96435409cd168736457dc9","tid":2157526,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200815/s00001/1597464208778/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2